<p>As a beginner, you need to learn the foundation movement patterns and develop the main physical attributes. These include muscular strength, endurance, muscle size, coordination, and mobility. Therefore, a well-organized approach is best.&nbsp;</p>



<p>To keep you on the right track, weâ€™ve listed the best dumbbell exercises for beginners below. Weâ€™ve included some <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/upper-body-dumbbell-workout" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">upper-body dumbbell workouts</a> and full-body functional movements. Letâ€™s take a look!</p>



<div class="wp-block-group ft-snippet is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
