<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Dumbbell-Bicep-Curl">Dumbbell Bicep Curl</h3>



<p>The <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/dumbbell-bicep-curl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">dumbbell bicep curl</a> uses a simple curling motion to bring the dumbbells to chest height. This isolates both heads of the biceps brachii muscles. Secondary movers include wrist flexors and wrist extensors.Â </p>



<p>Different grips and movement patterns can be used to change the exercise focus. With this, you have a versatile exercise that&#8217;s easy to learn and perform. It also works on grip strength, a <a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC10777545/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">key marker of health</a>.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio vimeo-custom"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
